title: [Ta'Illistim, Aerie Wey]
description: Several large warehouses stand nearby, constructed of sturdy granite blocks and boasting the city's trademark blue tiled roofs.  The blue-painted doors of the buildings are thrown open and workers hurry about moving boxes and crates of goods.

Several large warehouses stand nearby, constructed of sturdy granite blocks and boasting the city's trademark blue tiled roofs.  The blue-painted doors of the buildings are thrown open, though their high clerestory windows are barred.
